function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)
	
	nSpawnerRequestOn = nSpawnerRequestOn + 1

-- call the add parent event on linked spawners, then wait .5 seconds before checking parent/request again and spawning
-- (this is to cover an edge case where spawners could become active before all their parent spawners where cleared)
	if nSpawnerRequestOn == nSpawnerParents and bAddedSpawnParents == false then
		bAddedSpawnParents = true
		for i = 1, #tNextSpawners do
			Hydra.EventSendToActor("ADD_SPAWNER_PARENT", ID_THIS_QUEST, tNextSpawners[i])
		end
	end
	
	Hydra.Wait(0.5)
	
	if nSpawnerRequestOn == nSpawnerParents then
		Hydra.EventSendToActor("Start_Stage", ID_THIS_QUEST, ID_THIS_QUEST)
	end
	
end

function Start()
	
	for i, idActor in pairs(Hydra.ActorsInGroup("WE_Invasion_AllMonsters")) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idActor) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idActor) then
			Hydra.ActorKill(idActor)
			Hydra.Wait(Hydra.GetRandomFloat(0, .05))
		end
	end
	
	for i, idActor in pairs(Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "baseSpawner")) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsInGroup(idActor, "ZE_GatheringHorde_Spawners") then
			Hydra.ActorDisable(idActor)
		end
	end
	
	
	if mainQuest ~= nil then
		Hydra.EventSendToActor("AdvanceTier", idSelf, mainQuest)
	end
	
	Hydra.Wait(2)
	
	for i = 1, #tNextSpawners do
		Hydra.EventSendToActor("TURN_ON_SPAWNERS", ID_THIS_QUEST, tNextSpawners[i])
	end
	
end

function Start(idActor, fRange, idActorDetector)
	--end warmup timer early if all players are nearby
	if SetContains(tPlayers, idActor) == false then
		tPlayers[idActor] = 1
		nNearPlayerCount = nNearPlayerCount + 1
		if nNearPlayerCount >= Hydra.QuestGetParticipantCount() then
			bPlayersNear = true
			if bInRightPhase == true then
				Hydra.EventSendToActor("SpawnBoss", ID_THIS_QUEST, mainQuest)
			end
		end
	end
end

function Start(flTimeRemaining)
	bInRightPhase = true
	if bPlayersNear == true then
		Hydra.EventSendToActor("SpawnBoss", ID_THIS_QUEST, mainQuest)
	end
end

end

	captain = idActorSpawned
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(captain, false)
	Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(captain, false)
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(captain, ChannelPower)
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(captain, 10)
	Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(ZEBuffPower, "SHADOW_SHADER_BUFF", captain)
	captainBlocker = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "captainBlocker")[1]
--	Hydra.ActorsEnableLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "captainBlocker", true)
	
	idFXMarker = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(ACTOR_MARKERLOCATION, captainBlocker, false, 0, 0)
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(idFXMarker, 10)

end
